{"title":"linux安装ffmpeg","uid":"7378984146a7bb9fad07295c6edd9e2c","slug":"linux/blog/Linux安装ffmpeg","date":"2024-06-07T06:56:06.000Z","updated":"2024-06-07T07:55:01.590Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/linux/blog/Linux安装ffmpeg.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/zhouwenxing666/article/details/136321352\">https://blog.csdn.net/zhouwenxing666/article/details/136321352</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"nasm\"><a href=\"#nasm\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"nasm\"></a>nasm</h1><p>step1：window系统中打开链接<a href=\"https://www.linuxfromscratch.org/blfs/view/8.2/general/nasm.html\">NASM-2.13.03 (linuxfromscratch.org)</a><br>点击下图中红框下载</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SoarWithKite/image-hosting/main/linux/blog/image-20240606142105705.png\" alt=\"image-20240606142105705\"></p>\n<p>step2 将下载的tar.xz压缩包导入麒麟操作系统的 &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;ffmpeg 目录下（没有这个目录就先创建这个目录）</p>\n<p>tar -xf nasm-2.13.03.tar.xz</p>\n<p>.&#x2F;configure</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SoarWithKite/image-hosting/main/linux/blog/image-20240606142909427.png\" alt=\"image-20240606142909427\"></p>\n<p>make</p>\n<p>make install</p>\n<p>nasm -v</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SoarWithKite/image-hosting/main/linux/blog/image-20240606143135500.png\" alt=\"image-20240606143135500\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"安装yasm\"><a href=\"#安装yasm\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装yasm\"></a>安装yasm</h1><p>官网下载链接<a href=\"http://www.tortall.net/projects/yasm/releases/\">http://www.tortall.net/projects/yasm/releases/</a></p>\n<p>step1 点击下载，并放入麒麟OS的 &#x2F;usr&#x2F;loacl&#x2F;ffmpeg 路径下</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SoarWithKite/image-hosting/main/linux/blog/image-20240606143432275.png\" alt=\"image-20240606143432275\"></p>\n<p>tar -zxvf yasm-1.3.0.tar.gz</p>\n<p>cd yasm-1.3.0&#x2F;<br>.&#x2F;configure<br>make<br>make install</p>\n<p>yasm –version</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SoarWithKite/image-hosting/main/linux/blog/image-20240606143811146.png\" alt=\"image-20240606143811146\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"安装x264\"><a href=\"#安装x264\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装x264\"></a>安装x264</h1><p>官网链接：<a href=\"https://www.videolan.org/developers/x264.html\">https://www.videolan.org/developers/x264.html</a></p>\n<p>step1 进行官网，直接点击下载，将下载的tar.bz2压缩包放入麒麟操作系统 &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;ffmpeg&#x2F; 目录下</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SoarWithKite/image-hosting/main/linux/blog/image-20240606143916456.png\" alt=\"image-20240606143916456\"><br>tar -xvf x264-master.tar.bz2<br>cd x264-master<br>.&#x2F;configure –enable-shared<br>make<br>make install</p>\n<p>x264 –version</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SoarWithKite/image-hosting/main/linux/blog/image-20240606144657193.png\" alt=\"image-20240606144657193\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"安装ffmpeg\"><a href=\"#安装ffmpeg\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装ffmpeg\"></a>安装ffmpeg</h1><p>官网：<a href=\"https://www.ffmpeg.org/download.html#build-linux\">Download FFmpeg</a></p>\n<p>step1 进入官网，点击下图， 并选择适合自己的版本</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SoarWithKite/image-hosting/main/linux/blog/image-20240606144921369.png\" alt=\"image-20240606144921369\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SoarWithKite/image-hosting/main/linux/blog/image-20240606145143338.png\" alt=\"image-20240606145143338\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.ffmpeg.org/releases/\">https://www.ffmpeg.org/releases/</a></p>\n<p>选择困难症的话，可用点击链接 <a href=\"https://www.ffmpeg.org/releases/ffmpeg-5.1.2.tar.gz\">https://www.ffmpeg.org/releases/ffmpeg-5.1.2.tar.gz</a> 下载</p>\n<p>step2 将在window中下载的tar.gz压缩包 导入到麒麟OS系统中&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;ffmpeg&#x2F; 目录下</p>\n<p>step3 在麒麟OS终端，依次执行下面步骤</p>\n<p>cd &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;ffmpeg<br>tar -zxvf ffmpeg-5.1.2.tar.gz ##要是下载了bz2包 则使用该命令tar -xjvf ffmpeg-5.1.2.tar.bz2</p>\n<p>tar -xf ffmpeg-6.0.1-amd64-static.tar.xz</p>\n<p>cd ffmpeg-6.0.1-amd64-static&#x2F;<br>.&#x2F;ffmpeg -version</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SoarWithKite/image-hosting/main/linux/blog/image-20240606150733278.png\" alt=\"image-20240606150733278\"></p>\n<p>vim &#x2F;etc&#x2F;profile</p>\n<p>export HBASE_HOME&#x3D;&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;ffmpeg<br>export PATH&#x3D;$PATH:$HBASE_HOME&#x2F;ffmpeg-6.0.1-amd64-static</p>\n<p>source &#x2F;etc&#x2F;profile</p>\n","text":"https://blog.csdn.net/zhouwenxing666/article/details/136321352 nasmstep1：window系...","permalink":"/post/linux/blog/Linux安装ffmpeg","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.4k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Linux","slug":"Linux","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Linux.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#nasm\"><span class=\"toc-text\">nasm</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85yasm\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安装yasm</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85x264\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安装x264</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85ffmpeg\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安装ffmpeg</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"纸鸢","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://pic.aigexing.net/uploads/8/1253/2721999655/94139999534/5798514.jpg","link":"/","description":"早日退休","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"山海秘境","uid":"7569cb8aa9204affa256e2df9222ed57","slug":"roco/山海秘境","date":"2024-06-03T06:17:18.000Z","updated":"2024-06-07T07:07:22.852Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/roco/山海秘境.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"水系碧水灵兽除朱厌、夫诸 下面是神辅生成的自定义出招脚本:碧水灵兽 Lv.100 ( 1:水灵动 2:逍遥游 3:趁势击 4:雨飘摇 5:超级HP药剂 6:中瓶...","permalink":"/post/roco/山海秘境","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":566,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"t